729388f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Road - Dekalb Street
729388f-a.text:
Richmond Road, west side, between Dekalb Street
and Concord Place, showing General James Jourdan's house.
The property was owned by L. C. Butler in 1917.
About 1926
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
